videos.description: South Carolina's Evan Hinson comes away with a steal and sets up Justin Minaya for a layup.
videos.headline: Hinson turns defense into quick offense

videos.description: South Carolina's Chris Silva swings the ball to Frank Booker for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Booker converts from downtown

videos.description: South Carolina's Evan Hinson drives down the paint and converts a contested layup for a 3-point chance.
videos.headline: Hinson sinks tough lay-in for and-1 chance

videos.description: Frank Booker finds Hassani Gravett in the corner for a 3-pointer to extend South Carolina's lead to 13.
videos.headline: Gravett drains corner 3 to extend Gamecocks' lead

videos.description: Following a steal from South Carolina's Chris Silva, Frank Booker dishes to Justin Minaya in transition for the finger roll.
videos.headline: Booker sets up Minaya's transition lay-in

videos.description: Auburn's Chuma Okeke tries taking it inside for a layup but is denied by South Carolina's Chris Silva.
videos.headline: Silva executes chasedown block on Okeke

videos.description: Auburn's Horace Spencer leads Desean Murray inside for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Murray rattles rim with two-handed slam

videos.description: Auburn's Jared Harper finds a cutting Mustapha Heron for a big two-handed finish.
videos.headline: Heron soars on two-handed slam

videos.description: After grabbing the offensive rebound, Auburn's Horace Spencer tomahawks an emphatic one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Spencer throws down vicious putback dunk

videos.description: Auburn sophomore forward Anfernee McLemore lands awkwardly in the first half and is taken off the court of a stretcher. He was diagnosed with a dislocated ankle and is taken to the hospital.
videos.headline: McLemore stretchered off court with dislocated ankle

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McLemore stretchered off court with dislocated ankle) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Auburn's Desean Murray hauls in the offensive rebound and sinks a tough lay-in to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Murray nails contested layup for 3-point chance

videos.description: South Carolina's Maik Kotsar splits the defense and sinks a tricky layup to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Kotsar fires up Gamecocks' bench with tough lay-in

videos.description: The Gamecocks opened up a 46-25 first-half lead and didn't look back defeating the Tigers 84-75.
videos.headline: South Carolina upsets No. 10 Auburn

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (South Carolina upsets No. 10 Auburn) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: The Gamecocks hold on in the second half to beat the Tigers and earn a home win against a top-10 team for the first time since 2010.
videos.headline: South Carolina upsets No. 10 Auburn 84-75

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCB Highlight (South Car upsets Auburn) 180217 ESHEET
